flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: An approved category innovation initiative reaches the L4 activity 'form Collaboration Agreement With Suppliers' in the innovation pipeline.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers + STREAMS - Ingest initiative, SKU, supplier, forecast, inventory, and financial inputs]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast + RCA Service + Data Science - Analyze demand uplift, inventory impacts, and supplier risk/value]
  N2 --> N3{Agent: Process Builder - Agent Team (agentic_ai) + Rules IF node - Agentic recommendation of supplier and collaboration model}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: CWB Lifecycle + UI Screen - Human review and approval of recommended model]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Remote Functions + Process Builder (Action Item) - Execute agreements and operational writebacks]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Process Builder Notification + Cortex Monitoring + Dashboard (Subject Areas) - Notify stakeholders and monitor initiative KPIs]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Signed supplier collaboration agreements for prioritized initiatives, procurement and replenishment actions created in S4/TMS/WMS, tracked initiative KPIs (revenue uplift, EBITDA impact, working capital), and closed-loop monitoring for performance and rebalancing.]
  N3 -->|No supplier meets minimum innovation ...| B1[Agent Team initiates an open RFP subprocess (Process Builder - Dynamic Subprocess) and flags initiative for re-scoping]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Initiative paused for supplier discovery; timelines extended and RFP responses evaluated before re-issuing collaboration decision]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Supplier rejects proposed commercial/...| B2[Create negotiation Action Item and re-run negotiation simulation via Agent Team; update proposed terms and re-present for approval]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Agreement amended through negotiated terms or initiative downgraded if acceptable terms cannot be reached]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Projected financial impact below orga...| B3[Classify initiative as low-priority; monitor via Subject Areas and defer active contracting]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Resources conserved; initiative moves to a monitored pipeline until triggers or thresholds are met]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]